{"title":"Hexo Aurora 主题 LaTeX 数学公式渲染完整配置指南","uid":"cdaf287798a8886aaed8d059a065cece","slug":"hexo-aurora-latex-guide","date":"2025-08-16T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2025-08-17T04:23:57.174Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hexo-aurora-latex-guide.json","keywords":"blog, technology, programming","cover":"images/7.png","content":"<p>数学公式的准确且美观渲染是技术博客的重要需求。本文将详细介绍如何在 Hexo Aurora 主题中正确配置 LaTeX 数学公式渲染，解决常见的显示问题。</p>\n<h2 id=\"问题背景\"><a href=\"#问题背景\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"问题背景\"></a>问题背景</h2><p>在使用 Aurora 主题写技术文章时，经常遇到 LaTeX 公式无法正常渲染的问题：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>公式显示为原始的 <script type=\"math/tex\">...</script> 代码</li>\n<li>反斜杠 <code>\\</code> 被错误转义</li>\n<li>下划线 <code>_</code> 被渲染为斜体</li>\n<li>双竖线 <code>\\|</code> 显示异常</li>\n</ul>\n<p>经过深入研究和实践，找到了稳定可靠的解决方案。</p>\n<h2 id=\"技术栈对比\"><a href=\"#技术栈对比\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"技术栈对比\"></a>技术栈对比</h2><h3 id=\"常见方案比较\"><a href=\"#常见方案比较\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"常见方案比较\"></a>常见方案比较</h3><div class=\"table-container\">\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>技术栈</th>\n<th>优势</th>\n<th>劣势</th>\n<th>适用场景</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>hexo-renderer-markdown-it + markdown-it-katex</td>\n<td>语法现代、插件丰富</td>\n<td>Aurora主题兼容性差</td>\n<td>其他主题</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>hexo-renderer-kramed + hexo-filter-mathjax</td>\n<td>Aurora主题完美兼容</td>\n<td>需要手动修复转义规则</td>\n<td><strong>Aurora主题（推荐）</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>hexo-renderer-marked + hexo-math</td>\n<td>配置简单</td>\n<td>功能有限</td>\n<td>简单场景</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<h3 id=\"推荐方案：Kramed-MathJax\"><a href=\"#推荐方案：Kramed-MathJax\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"推荐方案：Kramed + MathJax\"></a>推荐方案：Kramed + MathJax</h3><p><strong>优势：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>✅ Aurora 主题原生支持</li>\n<li>✅ 渲染效果优秀，支持SVG输出</li>\n<li>✅ 性能良好，适合大量公式</li>\n<li>✅ 支持行内和行间公式</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>技术原理：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>hexo-renderer-kramed</code>：Markdown 渲染器，兼容 Aurora 主题</li>\n<li><code>hexo-filter-mathjax</code>：MathJax 过滤器，后处理数学公式</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"完整配置步骤\"><a href=\"#完整配置步骤\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"完整配置步骤\"></a>完整配置步骤</h2><h3 id=\"1-安装依赖包\"><a href=\"#1-安装依赖包\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. 安装依赖包\"></a>1. 安装依赖包</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 卸载可能冲突的渲染器</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">pnpm uninstall hexo-renderer-markdown-it hexo-renderer-mathjax</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 安装推荐的技术栈</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">pnpm install hexo-renderer-kramed hexo-filter-mathjax</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"2-修改-Hexo-配置\"><a href=\"#2-修改-Hexo-配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 修改 Hexo 配置\"></a>2. 修改 Hexo 配置</h3><p>编辑 <code>_config.yml</code>，添加 MathJax 配置：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># MathJax configuration (using kramed renderer)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">mathjax:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">enable:</span> <span class=\"literal\">true</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">per_page:</span> <span class=\"literal\">false</span>               <span class=\"comment\"># 不在每个页面加载，提高性能</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">tags:</span> <span class=\"string\">none</span>                    <span class=\"comment\"># 公式标签设置</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">single_dollars:</span> <span class=\"literal\">true</span>          <span class=\"comment\"># 支持单美元符号行内公式</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">cjk_width:</span> <span class=\"number\">0.9</span>               <span class=\"comment\"># 中文字符宽度</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">normal_width:</span> <span class=\"number\">0.6</span>            <span class=\"comment\"># 普通字符宽度</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">append_css:</span> <span class=\"literal\">true</span>             <span class=\"comment\"># 自动添加CSS</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">every_page:</span> <span class=\"literal\">false</span>            <span class=\"comment\"># 根据Front-matter决定是否加载</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"3-修复-Kramed-转义规则\"><a href=\"#3-修复-Kramed-转义规则\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3. 修复 Kramed 转义规则\"></a>3. 修复 Kramed 转义规则</h3><p>这是最关键的步骤！需要修复 kramed 的转义规则以支持 LaTeX 语法。</p>\n<h4 id=\"3-1-修改-inline-js\"><a href=\"#3-1-修改-inline-js\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.1 修改 inline.js\"></a>3.1 修改 inline.js</h4><p>找到文件：<code>node_modules/.pnpm/kramed@0.5.6/node_modules/kramed/lib/rules/inline.js</code></p>\n<p><strong>修改1：第11行 - 修复反斜杠转义</strong><br><figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 原始代码</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">escape</span>: <span class=\"regexp\">/^\\\\([\\\\`*&#123;&#125;\\[\\]()#$+\\-.!_&gt;])/</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 修改为（移除双反斜杠和花括号）</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">escape</span>: <span class=\"regexp\">/^\\\\([`*\\[\\]()# +\\-.!_&gt;])/</span>,</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p><strong>修改2：第20行 - 禁用下划线斜体</strong><br><figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 原始代码</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">em</span>: <span class=\"regexp\">/^\\b_((?:__|[\\s\\S])+?)_\\b|^\\*((?:\\*\\*|[\\s\\S])+?)\\*(?!\\*)/</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 修改为（只保留星号斜体）</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">em</span>: <span class=\"regexp\">/^\\*((?:\\*\\*|[\\s\\S])+?)\\*(?!\\*)/</span>,</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p><strong>修改3：第64行 - 修复竖线转义</strong><br><figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 原始代码</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">escape</span>: <span class=\"title function_\">replace</span>(inline.<span class=\"property\">escape</span>)(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;])&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&#x27;~|])&#x27;</span>)(),</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 修改为</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">escape</span>: <span class=\"title function_\">replace</span>(inline.<span class=\"property\">escape</span>)(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;])&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&#x27;~])&#x27;</span>)(),</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<h4 id=\"3-2-修改-renderer-js（可选：支持Todo-List）\"><a href=\"#3-2-修改-renderer-js（可选：支持Todo-List）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.2 修改 renderer.js（可选：支持Todo List）\"></a>3.2 修改 renderer.js（可选：支持Todo List）</h4><p>找到文件：<code>node_modules/.pnpm/kramed@0.5.6/node_modules/kramed/lib/renderer.js</code></p>\n<p>在第88行左右，替换 <code>listitem</code> 函数：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// Support To-Do List</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"title class_\">Renderer</span>.<span class=\"property\"><span class=\"keyword\">prototype</span></span>.<span class=\"property\">listitem</span> = <span class=\"keyword\">function</span>(<span class=\"params\">text</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"regexp\">/^\\s*\\[[x ]\\]\\s*/</span>.<span class=\"title function_\">test</span>(text)) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    text = text.<span class=\"title function_\">replace</span>(<span class=\"regexp\">/^\\s*\\[ \\]\\s*/</span>, <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&lt;input type=&quot;checkbox&quot;&gt;&lt;/input&gt; &#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">           .<span class=\"title function_\">replace</span>(<span class=\"regexp\">/^\\s*\\[x\\]\\s*/</span>, <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&lt;input type=&quot;checkbox&quot; checked&gt;&lt;/input&gt; &#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&lt;li style=&quot;list-style: none&quot;&gt;&#x27;</span> + text + <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&lt;/li&gt;\\n&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125; <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&lt;li&gt;&#x27;</span> + text + <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&lt;/li&gt;\\n&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"4-文章配置\"><a href=\"#4-文章配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4. 文章配置\"></a>4. 文章配置</h3><p>在需要使用数学公式的文章 Front Matter 中添加：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">---</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">title:</span> <span class=\"string\">你的文章标题</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">mathjax:</span> <span class=\"literal\">true</span>  <span class=\"comment\"># 启用MathJax渲染</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">---</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"5-验证配置\"><a href=\"#5-验证配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5. 验证配置\"></a>5. 验证配置</h3><p>重新生成站点：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"LaTeX-语法示例\"><a href=\"#LaTeX-语法示例\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"LaTeX 语法示例\"></a>LaTeX 语法示例</h2><h3 id=\"行内公式\"><a href=\"#行内公式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"行内公式\"></a>行内公式</h3><p>使用单个美元符号：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">这是行内公式 $E=mc^2$，可以嵌入文本中。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>渲染效果：这是行内公式 $E=mc^2$，可以嵌入文本中。</p>\n<h3 id=\"行间公式\"><a href=\"#行间公式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"行间公式\"></a>行间公式</h3><p>使用双美元符号：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$$</span><br><span class=\"line\">\\begin&#123;cases&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">x&#x27; = (x + y) \\mod N \\\\</span><br><span class=\"line\">y&#x27; = (x + 2y) \\mod N</span><br><span class=\"line\">\\end&#123;cases&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>渲染效果：</p>\n<script type=\"math/tex; mode=display\">\n\\begin{cases}\nx' = (x + y) \\mod N \\\\\ny' = (x + 2y) \\mod N\n\\end{cases}</script><h3 id=\"复杂公式示例\"><a href=\"#复杂公式示例\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"复杂公式示例\"></a>复杂公式示例</h3><figure class=\"highlight markdown\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Softmax 函数定义：</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">$$</span><br><span class=\"line\">\\text&#123;softmax&#125;(x<span class=\"emphasis\">_i) = \\frac&#123;\\exp(x_</span>i)&#125;&#123;\\sum<span class=\"emphasis\">_&#123;j=1&#125;^n \\exp(x_</span>j)&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">$$</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">数值稳定化版本：</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">$$</span><br><span class=\"line\">\\text&#123;softmax&#125;(x<span class=\"emphasis\">_i) = \\frac&#123;\\exp(x_</span>i - \\max<span class=\"emphasis\">_j x_</span>j)&#125;&#123;\\sum<span class=\"emphasis\">_&#123;k=1&#125;^n \\exp(x_</span>k - \\max<span class=\"emphasis\">_j x_</span>j)&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>渲染效果：</p>\n<p>Softmax 函数定义：</p>\n<script type=\"math/tex; mode=display\">\n\\text{softmax}(x_i) = \\frac{\\exp(x_i)}{\\sum_{j=1}^n \\exp(x_j)}</script><p>数值稳定化版本：</p>\n<script type=\"math/tex; mode=display\">\n\\text{softmax}(x_i) = \\frac{\\exp(x_i - \\max_j x_j)}{\\sum_{k=1}^n \\exp(x_k - \\max_j x_j)}</script><h2 id=\"常见问题排查\"><a href=\"#常见问题排查\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"常见问题排查\"></a>常见问题排查</h2><h3 id=\"问题1：公式不显示\"><a href=\"#问题1：公式不显示\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"问题1：公式不显示\"></a>问题1：公式不显示</h3><p><strong>检查清单：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"list-style: none\"><input type=\"checkbox\"></input> 确认安装了 <code>hexo-filter-mathjax</code></li>\n<li style=\"list-style: none\"><input type=\"checkbox\"></input> 文章 Front Matter 包含 <code>mathjax: true</code></li>\n<li style=\"list-style: none\"><input type=\"checkbox\"></input> <code>_config.yml</code> 中 MathJax 配置正确</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"问题2：反斜杠显示异常\"><a href=\"#问题2：反斜杠显示异常\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"问题2：反斜杠显示异常\"></a>问题2：反斜杠显示异常</h3><p><strong>原因：</strong> kramed 转义规则问题<br><strong>解决：</strong> 按照步骤3.1修改 <code>inline.js</code> 第11行</p>\n<h3 id=\"问题3：下划线被渲染为斜体\"><a href=\"#问题3：下划线被渲染为斜体\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"问题3：下划线被渲染为斜体\"></a>问题3：下划线被渲染为斜体</h3><p><strong>原因：</strong> Markdown 斜体语法冲突<br><strong>解决：</strong> 按照步骤3.1修改 <code>inline.js</code> 第20行</p>\n<h3 id=\"问题4：复杂公式渲染错误\"><a href=\"#问题4：复杂公式渲染错误\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"问题4：复杂公式渲染错误\"></a>问题4：复杂公式渲染错误</h3><p><strong>检查：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>确保公式语法正确</li>\n<li>避免使用不支持的LaTeX包</li>\n<li>测试简单公式确认基础配置正确</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"最佳实践\"><a href=\"#最佳实践\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"最佳实践\"></a>最佳实践</h2><h3 id=\"1-性能优化\"><a href=\"#1-性能优化\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. 性能优化\"></a>1. 性能优化</h3><figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># _config.yml</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">mathjax:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">per_page:</span> <span class=\"literal\">false</span>      <span class=\"comment\"># 仅在需要时加载</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">every_page:</span> <span class=\"literal\">false</span>    <span class=\"comment\"># 基于Front-matter控制</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"2-公式编写规范\"><a href=\"#2-公式编写规范\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 公式编写规范\"></a>2. 公式编写规范</h3><ul>\n<li>行内公式：用于简单表达式，如 $x+y$</li>\n<li>行间公式：用于复杂公式，独立成行显示</li>\n<li>使用 <code>\\text&#123;&#125;</code> 添加文字说明</li>\n<li>复杂公式考虑拆分为多个步骤</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"3-备份重要修改\"><a href=\"#3-备份重要修改\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3. 备份重要修改\"></a>3. 备份重要修改</h3><p>修改 node_modules 后建议：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 创建补丁文件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">cp</span> node_modules/.pnpm/kramed@0.5.6/node_modules/kramed/lib/rules/inline.js kramed-inline.patch.js</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">cp</span> node_modules/.pnpm/kramed@0.5.6/node_modules/kramed/lib/renderer.js kramed-renderer.patch.js</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>重新安装依赖时可快速恢复修改。</p>\n<h2 id=\"总结\"><a href=\"#总结\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"总结\"></a>总结</h2><p>通过本文的配置方法，你的 Hexo Aurora 博客现在可以：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>✅ 完美渲染 LaTeX 数学公式</li>\n<li>✅ 支持行内和行间公式</li>\n<li>✅ 正确处理反斜杠、下划线等特殊字符</li>\n<li>✅ 获得优秀的渲染性能和视觉效果</li>\n</ul>\n<p>这套方案经过实际项目验证，稳定可靠。如果你在配置过程中遇到问题，欢迎留言讨论！</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>参考资源：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/\">Hexo 官方文档</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://aurora.tridiamond.tech/\">Aurora 主题文档</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.mathjax.org/en/latest/\">MathJax 配置指南</a></li>\n</ul>\n","feature":true,"text":"解决Aurora主题LaTeX公式渲染问题的完整配置指南，包含技术栈选择、转义规则修复和实际测试验证。...","permalink":"/post/hexo-aurora-latex-guide","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"4.3k","symbolsTime":"4 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Tech","slug":"Tech","count":3,"path":"api/categories/Tech.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"hexo","slug":"hexo","count":2,"path":"api/tags/hexo.json"},{"name":"教程","slug":"教程","count":1,"path":"api/tags/教程.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF\"><span class=\"toc-text\">问题背景</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%A0%88%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94\"><span class=\"toc-text\">技术栈对比</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E6%AF%94%E8%BE%83\"><span class=\"toc-text\">常见方案比较</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%EF%BC%9AKramed-MathJax\"><span class=\"toc-text\">推荐方案：Kramed + MathJax</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%AD%A5%E9%AA%A4\"><span class=\"toc-text\">完整配置步骤</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E4%BE%9D%E8%B5%96%E5%8C%85\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1. 安装依赖包</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9-Hexo-%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE\"><span class=\"toc-tex